# Memory Bank

This project uses the **Memory Bank** pattern at @folder:docs/memory for persistent. Versioned context.

After work that materially affects behaviour, structure, tooling or conventions follow **memory-bank-update**: @file:.agents/skills/memory-bank-update/SKILL.md

Skip **Memory Bank** updates for trivial typos or tiny bugfixes unless they alter documented constraints or behaviour.

## How to Verify

### Confirm Memory Bank files are up to date

```bash
# Check that memory bank files were recently modified after a code change
git diff --name-only HEAD | grep "docs/memory/"

# Verify no memory bank file exceeds 200 lines
wc -l docs/memory/*.md
# Expected: all files ≤ 200 lines

# Confirm updated files reference real files/symbols that exist in the codebase
grep -rn "activeContext\|systemPatterns\|decisionLog\|techContext\|productContext\|projectbrief\|progress" docs/memory/ --include="*.md" | wc -l
# Expected: non-zero (cross-references exist between memory bank files)
```

